{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/Title_Eng.png?t=1730140030\" /><br>The Ministry's vaults store digital copies of every person. To investigate a simple murder, it would be enough to just talk to the victim's copy. However, for a case of national importance, you'll have to use the most recent and most terrifying technological advancements.<br><br>Plug someone's brain scan into one device and have a peaceful chat with them on neutral ground.<br><br>Plug them into something a little more unorthodox and see how they behave under pressure.<br><br>I could say that the choice is yours, but that would be a lie\u2014you will have to get your hands dirty one way or another.<br><br>A short (1-2 hour) linear narrative puzzle based on dialogues, plugging wires into devices, and messing with switches. If you always thought that the ending of 1984 could use a little more wiring puzzles, then this is the game for you.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/Major02.gif?t=1730140030\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/extras/Major01.gif?t=1730140030\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730140030","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/page.bg.jpg?t=1730140030","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730140030","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129400/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730140030","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://